high_descs: Take a left turn to exit the room and walk through the hallway to reach the room on the left to face the bed.
Pick up the green rag from the bed.
Turn around and enter the bathroom on the right to face the sink.
Wash the rag in the sink and pick it up.
Turn around to walk through the hallway to reach the bedroom on the right and face the table.
Put the rag on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed green rag on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and take right and walk into the last room.
Take the green rag on the bed.
then turn around and take left move on the bathroom washing basin and put the rag in the sink.
put the rag in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn around and take right then enter in to the first bedroom and place the rag on the right corner of the wooden table.
the rag is placed on the wooden table beside of apple.
anns.task_desc: put the rag on the wooden table.

high_descs: Go to the bed that is in this room.
Pick up the green towel on the bed.
Go in to the bathroom the second door on your right when you are in the hallway and put the towel in the sink.
Turn the water on to wet the towel and take it out of the sink.
Go in to the hallway take a right and enter the first door on your left and put the towel on the table next to the chair.
Look at the towel on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet towel on a bedroom table.

high_descs: Turn right,head towards the door, take right turn and move to the last room towards the bed.
Take the green cloth from the bed.
Turn around, take left towards the sink.
Wash the cloth in the wash basin.
Turn back, take right towards another bedroom
Place the cloth on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean Cloth on the Desk in the bed room

high_descs: Turn right. Exit the room. Turn right. When you reach the end, turn right. When you enter the room, turn right. When you reach the wall, turn left. Approach the bed.
Grab the cloth.
Turn around. Approach the wall. Turn left. Approach the wall. Turn left. As you exit into the hallway, turn right. Enter the next door on the right.
Place the cloth in the sink on the left. Open the faucets for 5 seconds. Turn off the faucets. Grab the cloth.
Turn around. When you exit into the hallway, turn right. Go ahead and turn left at the desk. Go inside and turn right.
Place the cloth on the desk towards the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Find a cloth, wet it and place it on a desk.

high_descs: Leave the room take a right and then a right into the last door and go to the bed.
Pick up the cloth on the bed.
Leave the room take a left and then the first right into the sink.
Put the cloth in the sink, turn the water on and take it out.
Leave the room take a right and then a left and to the desk.
Put the cloth on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed cloth on a desk.
